snippet.title: PERFECT - Guru Randhawa, Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari
snippet.description:
Sir to pairan de takk,
You so perfect! üíØ

Adding to the fire of ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, Guru Randhawa joins the party with PERFECT! üî• Composed and written by Guru Randhawa, Rony Ajnali and Gill Machhrai, the song is sung by Guru Randhawa. Starring our Sunny ‚ÄòVarun Dhawan‚Äô and Tulsi ‚ÄòJanhvi Kapoor‚Äô in the video, get ready to watch, vibe, and replay on loop! üöÄ

#PERFECT #GuruRandhawa #VarunDhawan #janhvikapoor 

Audio Credits:
Song - PERFECT
Singer - Guru Randhawa
Lyrics - Guru Randhawa , Gill Machhrai, Rony Ajnali
Composer - Guru Randhawa , Rony Ajnali, Gill Machhrai
Music Arranged by - Dilmaan

Assistant Styling: Priyanka Raman, Sanika Kukreja, Ishika Bhandari
Delhi Styling team: Khanak kasana, Tisha tawar
Hair - Ravi
Make up - Arveen Kaur

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

Audio on Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd (C) 2025

snippet.title: Vrusshabha Official Teaser | Mohanlal as a King | Directed by Nanda Kishore | Diwali 2025 Release
snippet.description:
#Vrusshabha #Mohanlal #Diwali2025 #VrusshabhaTeaser #RoarOfVrusshabha #ConnekktMedia #BalajiTelefilms #AbishekSVyasStudios #AashirvadCinemas

Welcome to the World of Vrusshabha.

A unique story brought to life through an unforgettable cinematic experience for global audiences. With Mohanlal playing a king for the very first time in a bilingual epic, Vrusshabha is a film that promises to stay with you long after you leave the theatre. Vrusshabha is a grand Pan Indian film shot simultaneously in Malayalam and Telugu, and dubbed in Hindi and Kannada.


Starring: Mohanlal, Samarjit Lankesh, Ragini Dwivedi

Crew:
Written and Directed by Nanda Kishore & Team

Presented by Connekkt Media and Balaji Telefilms in association with Abishek S Vyas Studios,
Produced by Shobha Kapoor, Ektaa R. Kapoor, C.K. Padma Kumar, Varun Mathur, Saurabh Mishra, Abishek S. Vyas, Praveer Singh, Vishal Gurnani, Juhi Parekh Mehta
Group CEO & CFO (BTL) : Sanjay Dwivedi 
Dialogues : SRK, Janardhan Maharshi, Karthik 
Music : Sam CS
Director of Photography : Antony Samson
Editor : K.M. Prakash
Sound Designers : Resul Pookutty (CAS, MPSE), Vijay Kumar (MPSE)
Co-Director : Shailendra Kumar K J
Associate Producer (BTL) : Janvi Gill
Group Head ‚Äì Commercial & Administration (BTL) : Hamavvand D. Chawda
Supervising Producer (BTL) : Shrey Jhawar
Production Designers : Nanditha Singh, Mohan B. Kere Action Directors : Peter Hein, Stunt Silva, Nikhil Costume Stylist : Harini Ramakrishna
Choreography : Kruti Mahesh
Re-Recording & Mix : Sarath Mohan
DI : Primefocus Ltd
Colorist : Andreas Brueckl (Andy)
Post Production Head (BTL) : Manohar Pandya
Makeup Chief : Jagdish Yera

VFX : Animantra VFX
Direction Department : Naresh Babu, Bharath Shivaraju, Ajay Shrinivas, Raghuraj Gowda
Assistant Editor : Rudresh Lake

snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Lower Bracket | Day 1
snippet.description:
The Lower Bracket of Battlegrounds Mobile India Showdown 2025 brings 24 teams into 4 days of intense battles, but only 12 will survive. Every match is do-or-die, where underdogs challenge giants and survival hangs by a thread.

Tune in live and cheer for your favourites as they fight to stay alive in BMSD 2025!

Lyrics :- 
Sath Pheron Se Bandha
Janmo Ka Ye Bandhan
Pyar Se Joda Hai Rabb Ne
Preet Ka Daman 
Hai Nayi Rasme, Nayi Kasame
Nayi Uljhan
Hont Hai Khamosh
Lekin Keh Rahi Dhakan

Tere naam ke harf ki tasbeeh ko, saanson
Ke gale ka haar kiya, duniya bhooli aur sirf
tujhe haan sirf tujhe hi pyar kiya

Tum jeet gaye hum hare, 
Tum jeet gaye hum hare, hum hare aur tum jeete
Mere dil ki dil se tauba, dil se tauba mere Dil ki
Dil ki tauba hai dil ab pyar dobara na hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Humne dhadkan dhadkan karke,
dil tere dil se jod liya
Ankhon ne ankhen padh padh ke, 
tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Tujhe pyaar kiya toh tu hi bata, hum ne kya koi jurm kiya
Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Dhadkan meri dhadkan

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, ‚ÄúDude, same!‚Äù 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that‚Äôs funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you‚Äôre laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you‚Äôre caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it‚Äôs a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.

snippet.description:
Watch the superhit "Swathilo Muthyam Antha" full video song from the classic Telugu movie Bangaru Bullodu (1993) on @mangomusic. Starring the legendary Nandamuri Balakrishna, alongside gorgeous actresses Raveena Tandon and Ramya Krishna, this melodious song is a timeless hit. The beautiful lyrics by Veturi and soulful music by Raj-Koti make this a must-watch. Movie directed by Raviraja Pinisetty and  Produced by  V. B. Rajendra Prasad under the banner Jagapathi Art Pictures.

This evergreen song is a fan favorite for its catchy tune and mesmerizing visuals. Relive the golden era of Telugu cinema with this iconic 90s love song.
